        "content": "<p>ricochet edited <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12781\">PR #12781</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Largely mechanical. The fixme in relation to <a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/WASI/issues/889\">WebAssembly/WASI#889</a> can be addressed after this lands.</p>\n<p>Non-exhaustive enums to variants has the largest surface area of changes (without <code>PartialEq</code> we use <code>matches</code>), and <code>Unknown</code> error is now <code>Other</code> for sockets and filesystem.</p>\n</blockquote>",
