    {
        "content": "<p>alexcrichton <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12781#issuecomment-4068231371\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12781\">PR #12781</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>One point (for onlookers, if any) is that this doesn't update the implementations of <code>wasi:random</code> or <code>wasi:http</code> for example to use new error codes. That's totally fine and makes this more reasonable to backport IMO, but I'll have a follow-up which implements those changes to take advantage of the APIs.</p>\n</blockquote>",
